	com_cli, Version 2.08

		Install Notes

This document describes how to build and install libCLI.a and libCOM.a.

1. Configuration

  Edit top directory "Imakefile.def" to fit your system. 
  Read comment lines carefully and set keywords properly.

2. Compilation

  Type as follows.

	% xmkmf -a
	% make

3. Install

  Create install directories where you wrote in "Imakefile.def"
  (INSTALL_LIB_PATH), and type 'make install'.

  After installing user command libraries, you can erase object files
  and libraries by typing 'make clean'.
